{"tid":1546031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"冰島拒絶「一帶一路」 彭斯點讚","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T13:00:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":511,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"d44c0922a2dba022d5eaa2985f12ee8cd87b1a3c","tid":1546031,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2440000/2444817/0905_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2440000%2F2444817%2F0905_1024.png&h=3030bea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯（Mike Pence）繼續在歐洲訪問，他昨訪問位於北極圈邊緣的冰島時表示，中國正積極擴大在北極地區的影響力，歡迎冰島拒絕中國「一帶一路」投資，並鼓勵冰島對中國電訊設備商華為說不。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，中國在經濟和戰略上都在北極地區變得更活躍，因此各國應該加強聯盟，團結抵制中國以及俄羅斯擴大地緣政治影響力的努力，包括對中國的「一帶一路」倡議和向華為說不。他又指出，任何一個擁抱華為技術和設備的自由國家都會產生嚴重問題。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯還談到當前的中美貿易戰，他說，美國將繼續對中國採取強硬立場，直到北京滿足華盛頓在結構改革方面的要求，包括開始承認管治冰島和美國以及全球各國互動的國際商業規則，「美國在與中國的自由、公平和對等貿易問題上立場堅定。」<br />\n<br />\n彭斯昨在冰島與冰島總統約翰內松（Guoni Johannesson）參加貿易投資圓桌會談，隨後還與冰島總理雅各布斯多蒂爾（Katrin Jakobsdottir）舉行雙邊會談。<br />\n<br />\n華府將要求北京有結構性改革<br />\n<br />\n值得注意，彭斯在歐洲訪問中不斷談及中國，除了昨日在冰島的言論，此前已和波蘭簽聲明將矛頭劍指華為，而之後在愛爾蘭則繼續遊說愛爾蘭和歐洲各國嚴防華為5G技術。根據白宮之前的聲明，彭斯此行的目的在於「應對中國惡意影響力的威脅，包括5G網絡的發展」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，《北京日報》旗下微信公眾號「長安街知事」今早評論，認為說服盟友對抗中國是訪問的主調，暗批彭斯是「反華急先鋒」。評論又將冰島總理雅各布斯多蒂爾一度表示有事不見彭斯，與彭斯「來者不善」扯上關係。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://china.hket.com/article/2444817</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8b49e13b0de9e0ee4f2d8a22d7ec159817ffe6ac","tid":1546031,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=cd4545b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"6c6cb0e43ea645a4c086c1f3731ad6bf6dc04cb2","tid":1546031,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:31:51.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce32ce17c0c04ad433ce337bc2c4cb74fb8dc113","tid":1546031,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313764cbe66ed11f5406f8bf52c10a4e1b77a39b","tid":1546031,"uid":251292,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:34:34.000Z","msg":"哇屌冰島都想搞？"},{"pid":"07722c260fa992f90ba0977549d55ccd70499d76","tid":1546031,"uid":45007,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:35:16.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n邊有文明國家會同你玩"},{"pid":"2015711d6a80b7f91d12df5a701db3fdab96566e","tid":1546031,"uid":318944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f201d4136b61e21d37e1508d3d5dedd8fa059404","tid":1546031,"uid":40250,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"冰島經過08年之後，知道經濟主權有幾重要"},{"pid":"450b89053c841f598aafa02e3358c97c27db33be","tid":1546031,"uid":28831,"like":